		<description>-Hide Widget Header</description>
		<description>-Hide Widget Header Text</description>
		<description>-Hide Spotlight Search (With auto height-adjustment!)</description>
		<description>-Custom Widget Page Wallpaper</description>
		<description>-Background Blur</description>
		<description>-Disable LS Padding</description>
		<description>-Disable LS Time Padding</description>
		<description>-Custom Edit Button Text</description>
		<description>-Square Edit Button</description>
		<description>-Transparent Edit Button</description>
		<description>-Custom Footer Text Color</description>
